CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 16, 1954, pg. 6, reads: "Carver Luncheon - The tenth annual observance of George Washington Carver Week was highlighted with a luncheon at the Sheraton Hotel on Wednesday. The Schenley High School Chorus, under the direction of J. Howard Keister, provided several selections..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Schenley High School Chorus, singing at George Washington Carver luncheon, Penn-Sheraton Hotel
